{"tid":1362792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想727去元朗既請入黎","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T05:57:11.000Z","uid":11904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25aacc2ae872753a03c9d6e4567aca11d5b6d18c","tid":1362792,"uid":11904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQgYsQh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQgYsQh.png&h=9f193e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，多謝大家又一次準備出發去抗爭<br />\n但係，今次最缺乏既係<span style=\"color: red;\">實際既資訊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如果你係想去既一位</span></span>，請付出少少行動，<span style=\"color: gold;\">主動啲開/推post，上網/落街做文宣工作</span>，將727既時間地點，話比多啲人知，人數係保護大家既重要因素。 未確定好既資訊就一齊討論好佢！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係唔想去既一位</span></span>，戰友們唔會介意，但希望唔好不停開post叫人唔好去，<span style=\"color: gold;\">反而可以推下728上環既post</span><br />\n<br />\n因為...<br />\n宜家就好似當時企係立會前，有人想衝，有人反對<br />\n今次大家最體驗到合作既力量就係，即使你唔贊成衝，都一樣會支持戰友既決定<br />\n<br />\n希望大家會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">尊重同支持</span></span>打算去元朗既戰友<br />\n唔出席都可以支持<br />\n唔出席都可以幫手搞728，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係上環再見返大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就係有呢種力量，大家先更體驗到自己係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span></span>既意識<br />\n大家要繼續努力，走失左無所謂，要拉返你既戰友返返入隊呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山</span>，並唔係一句口號，唔係嗌完就算<br />\n重點係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各 有 各 做</span>，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實行</span>各種唔同方法同策略一齊去去推倒一個腐敗既政權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fdd7989c54cf83244c519e005b0976df940c17e2","tid":1362792,"uid":11904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\